  "body": "# Spring Flowers\n**Hi!**\n\nI wanted to create a pack with variated flowers for a long time, and it's here!\n\n**In this pack you have:**\n\n- 5 additional variants for each small flower,\n- 6 rare, historical flowers,\n- 5 additional variants for a rose bush, peony, lilac,\n- 11 additional variants for sunflower 🌻\n\n**Check out gallery, to see all flowers!**\n\n<hr>\n\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/l3AUlfG.png\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kC49wDD.png\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/UeySBKd.png\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iFi8Zc6.png\">\n\n\n\n<hr>\n\n**Hope you like it!**\n\n<hr>\n\n© 2020 Daggsy ∘ [CC-BY-NC-ND](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/)",
